`aioflo` is a Python 3, `asyncio`-friendly library for interacting with
[Flo by Moen Smart Water Detectors](https://www.moen.com/flo).

# Python Versions

`aioflo` is currently supported on:

* Python 3.6
* Python 3.7
* Python 3.8

# Installation

```python
pip install aioflo
```

